        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324588" xml:id="d1e168996">Henricus Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e168998">Augustudunensis</placeName> episcopus</persName> tam futuris quam
                    presentibus notum facio quod <persName key="d1e30079" xml:id="d1e169002">Richardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e169004">Curte
                            Rabodi</placeName>
                    </persName> gravi apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324453" xml:id="d1e169007">Fontenetense monasterium</placeName> infirmitate detentus mortemque sibi
                    suspicans imminere, divine tamdem visitationis inspiratione compunctus quod
                    ejusdem loci fratres diu multumque sine causa vexasset, satisfacere statuens
                    dedit eis pro anima sua et antecessorum suorum quicquid ipsius erat in loco qui
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325253" xml:id="d1e169010">
                        <foreign>Curtresum</foreign>
                    </placeName> dicitur juxta quod subscripti declarant termini. A rupe videlicet
                    que ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325218" xml:id="d1e169014">ulmum <persName key="d1e30085" xml:id="d1e169016">Sebaldi</persName>
                    </placeName> incipit usque ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325073" xml:id="d1e169020">boscum <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324443" xml:id="d1e169022">Eperi</placeName>
                    </placeName> et <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325189" xml:id="d1e169025">rivum
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325299" xml:id="d1e169027">Jalegni</placeName>
                    </placeName>. Itemque a rivo sicut ipse fluit usque ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325230" xml:id="d1e169030">viam publicam</placeName>, a via
                    autem sicut ipsa ducit usque in fines <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e169033">Marmanie</placeName>. Porro ab ipsis finibus per rupem
                    quamdam nativam que est in <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325104" xml:id="d1e169036">cumba, cui nomen Villamontosi</placeName>, usque ad prefatam <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325218" xml:id="d1e169039">ulmum Sebaldi</placeName>. Dedit
                    preterea quicquid illi erat alodii in villa seu finibus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324455" xml:id="d1e169043">Fraxini</placeName>, chasamentum
                    quoque cum a dominis tamen adquirere potuerint. Dedit etiam de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325062" xml:id="d1e169046">adjacente abbatie
                        foresta</placeName> ligna ad calefaciendum perpetuo furnum necessaria. Huic
                    donationi ejus testes affuerunt qui subnotati sunt <persName key="d1e30091" xml:id="d1e169049">Andreas <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e169051">Montis Barri</placeName> dominus</persName>,
                        <persName key="d1e30097" xml:id="d1e169055">Vido de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324374" xml:id="d1e169057">
                            <foreign>Venerri</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30104" xml:id="d1e169061">Rogerius patruus
                        ejus</persName>, <persName key="d1e30110" xml:id="d1e169064">Viardus
                            <persName key="d1e30116" xml:id="d1e169066">Oliverii filius</persName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30122" xml:id="d1e169070">Symon de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324438" xml:id="d1e169072">
                            <foreign>Curtengi</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30128" xml:id="d1e169076">Hugo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e169078">Plaaneto</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30134" xml:id="d1e169081">Bernardus <addName>
                            <foreign>Nariouz</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30141" xml:id="d1e169087">Calo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e169089">
                            <foreign>Grinum</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30147" xml:id="d1e169093">Bernardus <addName>
                            <foreign>Braibanzuns</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30153" xml:id="d1e169099">Christianus <addName>
                            <foreign>Erlauz</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, multique alii qui ad eum visitandum convenerant.</p>
